<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC8">
<l>aruḷ koṇṭāṭum aṭiyavar iṉpuṟa</l>
<l>aruḷiṉāṉ avaru maṟaiyiṉ poruḷ</l>
<l>aruḷkoṇṭāyiram iṉ tamiḻ pāṭiṉāṉ</l>
<l>aruḷ kaṇṭīrivvulakiṉil mikkatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See the abundant grace in this world of him [Nammalvar]</l>
<l>who graciously spoke the meaning of that rare veda,</l>
<l>so that it produced pleasure for the devotees who praise the grace [of the Lord],</l>
<l>of him who sang the thousand sweet Tamil [verses].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
